Namootni nu jaallannu mootummaa Waaqatti ilaalu danda’uu, kallatti ulfina qabeessa Waaqa irraa, ha ta’uu malee irra caalaan isaa waa’ee Waaqayyoti, waa’een keenya immoo hanga xiqqaa dha.
Ammam gammachuun ta’a, namoota jaallannu wajjin immoo walitti dhufuu fi Waaqayyoon waaqessuu, isaanii wajjin, bara baraan.
